 games Believe it or not, this was the first time athletes could attend the closing ceremony, and more than 6,000 marched into the stadium as part of the show.\", \"from\": 1940, \"to\": 2134, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Date\", \"from\": 1940, \"to\": 1944}, {\"ngram\": \"host city\", \"from\": 1949, \"to\": 1958}, {\"ngram\": \"2028 summer games\", \"from\": 1963, \"to\": 1980}, {\"ngram\": \"the first time athletes\", \"from\": 2009, \"to\": 2032}, {\"ngram\": \"the closing ceremony\", \"from\": 2046, \"to\": 2066}, {\"ngram\": \"the stadium\", \"from\": 2101, \"to\": 2112}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 2116, \"to\": 2120}, {\"ngram\": \"the show\", \"from\": 2124, \"to\": 2132}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There was also a fantastic display of Buchaechum (traditional Korean fan dance) to hand over to Seoul for the 1988 Games.\", \"from\": 2135, \"to\": 2256, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2174, \"end\": 2184, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Buchaechum\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Buchaechum\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Buchaechum\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Buchaechum\"}, {\"begin\": 2198, \"end\": 2204, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Korean_language\", \"score\": 0.9999982200163157, \"rank\": 9.484526037191358e-07, \"text\": \"Korean\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Korean_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Korean_language\"}, {\"begin\": 2232, \"end\": 2237, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seoul\", \"score\": 0.9999751958237005, \"rank\": 2.4804617255338342e-05, \"text\": \"Seoul\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seoul\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seoul\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a fantastic display\", \"from\": 2150, \"to\": 2169}, {\"ngram\": \"the 1988 Games\", \"from\": 2241, \"to\": 2255}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A festival of planets, stars, fireworks and monsters?\", \"from\": 2258, \"to\": 2311, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A festival\", \"from\": 2258, \"to\": 2268}, {\"ngram\": \"planets\", \"from\": 2272, \"to\": 2279}, {\"ngram\": \"stars\", \"from\": 2281, \"to\": 2286}, {\"ngram\": \"fireworks\", \"from\": 2288, \"to\": 2297}, {\"ngram\": \"monsters\", \"from\": 2302, \"to\": 2310}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hell yes.\", \"from\": 2312, \"to\": 2321, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"One of the main events in Barcelona's closing ceremony was a stadium-wide display of flames, dancers and striking costumes, and it looked like quite the party.\", \"from\": 2322, \"to\": 2481, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2349, \"end\": 2358, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barcelona\", \"score\": 0.9779503233342209, \"rank\": 0.022546826743001926, \"text\": \"Barcelona\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barcelona\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barcelona\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the main events\", \"from\": 2329, \"to\": 2344}, {\"ngram\": \"a stadium-wide display\", \"from\": 2381, \"to\": 2403}, {\"ngram\": \"flames\", \"from\": 2407, \"to\": 2413}, {\"ngram\": \"dancers\", \"from\": 2415, \"to\": 2422}, {\"ngram\": \"striking costumes\", \"from\": 2427, \"to\": 2444}, {\"ngram\": \"quite the party\", \"from\": 2465, \"to\": 2480}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Samba music, carnival dancers and huge smatterings of colour?\", \"from\": 2483, \"to\": 2544, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Samba music\", \"from\": 2483, \"to\": 2494}, {\"ngram\": \"carnival dancers\", \"from\": 2496, \"to\": 2512}, {\"ngram\": \"huge smatterings\", \"from\": 2517, \"to\": 2533}, {\"ngram\": \"colour\", \"from\": 2537, \"to\": 2543}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There is not much more we could ask for from Rio's closing ceremony, and the rhythmic, pulsing show was one hell of a fun close to what was a fantastic Olympics.\", \"from\": 2545, \"to\": 2706, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2591, \"end\": 2594, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"score\": 0.9994415079068741, \"rank\": 0.0005588041806473999, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the rhythmic, pulsing show\", \"from\": 2618, \"to\": 2644}, {\"ngram\": \"one hell\", \"from\": 2649, \"to\": 2657}, {\"ngram\": \"a fun\", \"from\": 2661, \"to\": 2666}, {\"ngram\": \"a fantastic Olympics\", \"from\": 2685, \"to\": 2705}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is definitely the most vibrant ceremony on the list.\", \"from\": 2707, \"to\": 2764, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the most vibrant ceremony\", \"from\": 2726, \"to\": 2751}, {\"ngram\": \"the list\", \"from\": 2755, \"to\": 2763}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Aussies really know how to do fireworks, do not they?\", \"from\": 2766, \"to\": 2823, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Aussies\", \"from\": 2766, \"to\": 2777}, {\"ngram\": \"fireworks\", \"from\": 2800, \"to\": 2809}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While Sydney's closing ceremony was an all-round showstopper, the fireworks were undoubtedly the highlight.\", \"from\": 2824, \"to\": 2931, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2831, \"end\": 2837, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"score\": 0.9999608625567858, \"rank\": 3.9130626070874295e-05, \"text\": \"Sydney\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an all-round showstopper\", \"from\": 2860, \"to\": 2884}, {\"ngram\": \"the fireworks\", \"from\": 2886, \"to\": 2899}, {\"ngram\": \"the highlight\", \"from\": 2917, \"to\": 2930}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Firework artists from all five competing continents took part, and the display over the stadium was quite a sight.\", \"from\": 2932, \"to\": 3046, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Firework artists\", \"from\": 2932, \"to\": 2948}, {\"ngram\": \"all five competing continents\", \"from\": 2954, \"to\": 2983}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 2989, \"to\": 2993}, {\"ngram\": \"the display\", \"from\": 2999, \"to\": 3010}, {\"ngram\": \"the stadium\", \"from\": 3016, \"to\": 3027}, {\"ngram\": \"quite a sight\", \"from\": 3032, \"to\": 3045}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We can never forget that sparkly silver great white shark.\", \"from\": 3047, \"to\": 3105, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that sparkly silver great white shark\", \"from\": 3067, \"to\": 3104}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As the hopeful, comforting vocals of the late John Lennon hummed over London's Olympic Stadium, it was a demonstration of a more understated, but still just as impactful, approach to the finale of the Olympics.\", \"from\": 3107, \"to\": 3317, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3154, \"end\": 3165, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Lennon\", \"score\": 0.9999999815427147, \"rank\": 1.8457331452818375e-08, \"text\": \"John Lennon\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Lennon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Lennon\"}, {\"begin\": 3178, \"end\": 3184, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999262828979554, \"rank\": 7.372232266727178e-05, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"As the hopeful, comforting vocals\", \"from\": 3107, \"to\": 3140}, {\"ngram\": \"a demonstration\", \"from\": 3210, \"to\": 3225}, {\"ngram\": \"approach\", \"from\": 3278, \"to\": 3286}, {\"ngram\": \"the finale\", \"from\": 3290, \"to\": 3300}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 3304, \"to\": 3316}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's definitely one of our faves.\", \"from\": 3318, \"to\": 3351, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our faves\", \"from\": 3341, \"to\": 3350}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Beijing's opening ceremony was our favourite of all time, but the year of rehearsals that went into the 2008 Olympics send-off certainly paid off, too.\", \"from\": 3353, \"to\": 3504, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3354, \"end\": 3361, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9977063921442739, \"rank\": 0.002298880586038952, \"text\": \"Beijing\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our favourite\", \"from\": 3384, \"to\": 3397}, {\"ngram\": \"all time\", \"from\": 3401, \"to\": 3409}, {\"ngram\": \"the year\", \"from\": 3415, \"to\": 3423}, {\"ngram\": \"rehearsals\", \"from\": 3427, \"to\": 3437}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2008 Olympics send-off\", \"from\": 3453, \"to\": 3479}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A sea of vibrantly-dressed dancers performing impeccably in sync choreography was striking.\", \"from\": 3505, \"to\": 3596, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A sea\", \"from\": 3505, \"to\": 3510}, {\"ngram\": \"vibrantly-dressed dancers\", \"from\": 3514, \"to\": 3539}, {\"ngram\": \"sync choreography\", \"from\": 3565, \"to\": 3582}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Given the Olympics were born out of Ancient Greece, it's hardly surprising that Athens knows how to close them with a bang.\", \"from\": 3598, \"to\": 3721, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3635, \"end\": 3649, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ancient_Greece\", \"score\": 0.9999262612572151, \"rank\": 5.3409166734912176e-05, \"text\": \"Ancient Greece\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ancient_Greece\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ancient_Greece\"}, {\"begin\": 3679, \"